<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.8">
<l>nāḻikai kūṟiṭṭuk kāttuniṉṟa varacarkaḷ tammukappē</l>
<l>nāḻikaipō kappaṭaipo rutavaṉtē vakitaṉ ciṟuva</l>
<l>ṉāḻikoṇṭaṉ ṟiravima ṟaippac cayattira taṉtalaiyai</l>
<l>pāḻiluru ḷappaṭaipo rutavaṉpak kamēkaṇ ṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The child of Devakī,</l>
<l rend="indent"> who fought with weapons so that the hours passed</l>
<l>in front of the kings who stood guard hour after hour –</l>
<l>there are those who saw [him]</l>
<l rend="indent">at the side of he who fought with weapons</l>
<l>when [he] hid the sun with [his] discus that day</l>
<l rend="indent">so that Jayadratha’s head rolled into the waste land.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
